# Concept

This project converts a Word requirements document (.docx) into three deliverables:

1) Decompose (User Stories)
- Outputs a stories array
- Each story includes: id, module, feature, title, user_story, acceptance_criteria, priority, dependencies, notes

2) Schedule (User Story Map)
- Outputs backbone + releases + themes
- themes.story_ids reference story ids from decomposition

3) Estimate (Standard estimation table)
- For each story: complexity, dev/test/PM days, risk, assumptions

The frontend handles interaction and visualization. The backend parses Word, generates JSON, and (optionally) calls an OpenAI-compatible LLM.
